---
layout: layout.njk
title: Home | Auto Blogger
---

<div class="hero">
  <h1>The Future of AI & Tech</h1>
  <p>Exploring the latest in Artificial Intelligence, programming, and technology trends. Fully automated and written by AI, delivered weekly.</p>
</div>

<div class="post-list">
  {%- for post in collections.posts | reverse -%}
    <a href="{{ post.url | url }}" class="post-card">
      <h2>{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
      <div class="date">{{ post.date | postDate }}</div>
      <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
    </a>
  {%- endfor -%}
</div>
